<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> tribhu</hi>vaṉa viratevaṟku yāṇṭu nālāvatu kāttikai mātam kuṟuppu ṉāṭṭu vicaiyama<unclear>ṅkalat</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tu perumāḷ<unclear>re</unclear>valkaḷil kecittiruvuṭai<unclear>yā</unclear>ṉ vicaiyamaṅkalattu Āḷuṭaiyār tirunāki<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>mu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭaiyāṟku caṉtiyā tipam yiraṇṭukku Oṭukkiṉa Accu Iraṇṭu <unclear>yivacciraṇṭuṅ</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>ṭom Ikkoyil kāṇiuṭaiya civappirāmaṇan Ā<hi rend="grantha">tra</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>go</unclear>tra</hi>ttu Āḷavaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
