<lb n="6"/>rippomākavum kuṭaṅko<unclear>ṇ</unclear>ṭu koyil pukuvāṉ Erippatākavum Ittaṉmam paṉ<hi rend="grantha">māheśvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi>
